description: Information on Citibike stations, including availability, capacity, and operational status, supporting insights into bike-sharing usage and infrastructure.

metadata.description: Unique identifier for each bike station.
The full name of the bike station, indicating its location.
Abbreviated name for the bike station, used for quick reference.
Geographical latitude of the bike station; Indicates the north-south position on the Earth's surface.
Geographical coordinate indicating the east-west position of the bike station.
Identifier for the geographical region where the bike station is located.
Methods available for renting bikes at the station; Includes options like KEY and CREDITCARD.
Total number of bike docks available at the station.
Indicates whether the bike station is equipped with a key dispenser for bike rentals.
The number of bikes currently available for rental at the station.
Number of bikes that are currently out of service at the station.
Number of available docking spaces for bikes at the station.
Number of bike docks that are currently out of service at the station.
Indicates whether the bike station is currently installed and operational.
Indicates whether the bike station is currently available for renting bikes.
Indicates whether the bike station is currently accepting bike returns.
Indicates whether the bike station has available keys for rental.
Timestamp indicating the last time the station's status was updated, formatted in UTC.
